reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Some of the figures needs more work.
reviews.reviewText: The Super Hero Adventures figure set is really fun for my kids. It has 26 small superhero toys. They love playing with them and we also use them to decorate birthday cakes. The toys are just the right size for kids to hold and play with. They are also good for giving away as party favors or as prizes at school. I have to say some of the figures had some cosmetic issues but over all good.
